data.text:
Inmate Search

Below is a list of Black Hawk County, Iowa inmates currently in custody.

An arrest without disposition is not an indication of guilt. Individuals shown in any capacity on these pages are considered innocent until proven guilty by a court of law. Individuals who are in jail or released from jail do not necessarily prove guilt or innocence.
